Text: MidContinent Maps Cc Hey everyone We are having the map guys make maps for each state in our region including Ontario These are the items we would like to see on the maps If you can think of anything else you would like to see please let me know today The sooner we get this list to them the sooner they will begin building our maps Any input would be greatly appreciated Thanks Lindsay Current and Proposed Cogens MunicipalsCoops Power Plants Substations Power Lines NG Pipes LNG Facilities and Pipelines Utility Service Areas LDC and Electric Storage Fields Lindsay Culotta Enron North America Phone Fax

FW Energy AtlasPlease take a look at these maps and let me know what you think so that I can let the map guys know if we want to make any changes Thanks Lindsay Original Message From Hawkins Craig Sent Friday October PM To Culotta Lindsay Subject Energy Atlas Lindsay I have saved the requested Energy Atlas maps on ODropboxfraleyPDFzip I have included all of them except for OhioIOU OhioLDC Ontario Central and Ontario Western I am having some technical problems with exporting PDFs for these files Please look them over and let me know what you think Thanks and have a great weekend Craig Hawkins
